DESCRIPTION:If you're a robotics enthusiast or computer vision engineer who loves tinkering with edge devices, the Jetson AI Research Lab Call is the community space you've been looking for.\n\nThis is an open, collaborative call where Jetson enthusiasts gather to showcase projects, problem-solve technical issues, brainstorm the future of edge AI, computer vision, and agent deployment, and connect around hiring opportunities.\n\nMicrosoft Teams Meeting\nJoin the meeting now: https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19%3ameeting_ZWUwNTIxYmQtNGJmZC00MDA1LTkzN2MtYmFmMzJjZWUxNDFh%40thread.v2/0?context=%7b%22Tid%22%3a%2243083d15-7273-40c1-b7db-39efd9ccc17a%22%2c%22Oid%22%3a%223e5863c5-26ea-489e-a546-cdc43df532ed%22%7d\n\nMeeting ID: 288 976 487 014 3\nPasscode: 6oG2uK2A\nDial-in: +1 949-570-1120,,369799951#\nPhone conference ID: 369 799 951#\nTenant key: teams@vc.nvidia.com\nVideo ID: 114 238 807 7
